description: Differential gene expression analysis based on the negative binomial distribution
homepage_url: https://www.bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/DESeq2.html
long_description: |
  Estimate variance-mean dependence in count data from high-throughput sequencing assays and
  test for differential expression based on a model using the negative binomial distribution
